の関係者の強みを結集し、社会課題解…", "…ては、省内外の関係者の強みを結集し、社会課題解決型の事業も含め、スタートアップ創出を全力で後押ししていく、こういう役割を持っておりますので、…", "…で後押ししていく、こういう役割を持っておりますので、先生御提案のソーシャルスタートアップについてもこの推進室でしっかり対応したいと思います。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01020220309/237", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01020220309/257", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01020220309/268", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01020220309/270", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01020220309/272", "sentence": []}]}]}, {"date": "2022-03-16", "meeting": [{"meeting_name": "衆議院 経済産業委員会", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/17", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/29", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/39", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/42", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/46", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/62", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/74", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/80", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/82", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/88", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/92", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/100", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/102", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/104", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/106", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120804080X00420220316/125", "sentence": []}, {"url": "ht